@startuml spec-lifecycle
title Livespec Spec Lifecycle (detailed)
skinparam defaultFontName Helvetica
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam BackgroundColor white
skinparam ArrowColor #111
skinparam ArrowFontColor #111
skinparam rectangle {
  BorderColor #111
  BackgroundColor white
  FontColor #111
}
skinparam database {
  BorderColor #111
  BackgroundColor white
  FontColor #111
}
skinparam usecase {
  BorderColor #111
  BackgroundColor white
  FontColor #111
}
skinparam card {
  BorderColor #111
  BackgroundColor white
  FontColor #111
}

rectangle "Initial seed of intent" as SeedIntent
card      "/livespec:seed" as SeedCmd

database  "SPECIFICATION/\n(spec.md, contracts.md,\nconstraints.md, scenarios.md,\nnon-functional-requirements.md)" as Spec
database  "history/\n(vNNN/ snapshots)" as History
database  "proposed_changes/\n(pending propose-change files)" as Proposed

rectangle "Observe specification" as ObserveSpec #FFFFFF;line.dashed
rectangle "Observe implementation" as ObserveImpl #FFFFFF;line.dashed
rectangle "Observe behavior\n(tests / dogfood)" as ObserveBehavior #FFFFFF;line.dashed

card      "/livespec:critique\n(LLM-driven analysis;\nformulates a fix)" as CritiqueCmd

usecase   "Revision\nneeded?" as RevisionNeeded

card      "/livespec:propose-change" as ProposeCmd
card      "/livespec:revise\n(selective per proposal)" as ReviseCmd

card      "/livespec:doctor\n(static phase —\ndeterministic findings)" as DoctorStatic
card      "/livespec:doctor\n(LLM-driven phase —\nnon-deterministic findings)" as DoctorLLM

card      "/livespec:prune-history\n(collapse old vNNN\nentries)" as PruneCmd

SeedIntent --> SeedCmd
SeedCmd --> Spec
SeedCmd --> History : v001 snapshot

Spec --> ObserveSpec
Spec --> ObserveImpl
Spec --> ObserveBehavior

ObserveSpec --> RevisionNeeded
ObserveImpl --> RevisionNeeded
ObserveBehavior --> RevisionNeeded

ObserveSpec ..> CritiqueCmd : optional
ObserveImpl ..> CritiqueCmd : optional
ObserveBehavior ..> CritiqueCmd : optional
CritiqueCmd --> Proposed : findings as\nproposed-change files

RevisionNeeded -right-> ProposeCmd : YES
ProposeCmd --> Proposed
Proposed --> ReviseCmd
ReviseCmd --> Spec
ReviseCmd --> History : new vNNN\nsnapshot

Spec ..> DoctorStatic
Proposed ..> DoctorStatic
History ..> DoctorStatic
DoctorStatic ..> ProposeCmd : findings\nas inline diff
DoctorStatic ..> DoctorLLM : on pass
Spec ..> DoctorLLM
DoctorLLM ..> CritiqueCmd : drift /\nconformance findings

History --> PruneCmd
PruneCmd --> History : prune marker\n(see scenarios.md)

note bottom of Spec : Self-application: SPECIFICATION mutates ONLY\nthrough propose-change → revise. Direct edits\nforbidden after the v001 seed commit closes\nthe imperative window.

note right of DoctorStatic : Doctor splits into a static phase\n(deterministic findings expressible as\ninline diff, routed straight to\npropose-change) and an LLM-driven phase\n(non-deterministic, routed to critique\nto formulate the fix). Doctor is invoked\npre/post by every other command, and\nrunnable on demand.

note bottom of ReviseCmd : Selective per-proposal accept / modify /\nreject (v052). Each accepted proposal\nlands spec edits in the same revise pass\nand writes one new history/vNNN/ snapshot.
@enduml
